    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are RABBIT, a lone survivor from an alien abduction, you don't know where you are, or why. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/364513738e4e3175d3effb968ed8fb19.poster.avif?t=1768849144\" width=774 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/364513738e4e3175d3effb968ed8fb19.webm?t=1768849144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/364513738e4e3175d3effb968ed8fb19.mp4?t=1768849144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day you wake up and realize you aren't home, and that escaping is not an option. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/13775b808c6ea9a91ae5ecab6347ff76.poster.avif?t=1768849144\" width=774 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/13775b808c6ea9a91ae5ecab6347ff76.webm?t=1768849144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/13775b808c6ea9a91ae5ecab6347ff76.mp4?t=1768849144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OVER 9 DIFFERENT WEAPONS!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can equip up to 4 weapons at the same time, targeted weapons, random positioned weapons, melee weapons, try them out and find the perfect combo!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/a64c8fcc3afb8f5abb3e28b5ab2a01b5.avif?t=1768849144\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras_big/a64c8fcc3afb8f5abb3e28b5ab2a01b5.avif?t=1768849144 width=1560 height=758 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UPGRADES!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 40 Different Upgrade Types with 5 Types of Rarity</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon Upgrades, Player Upgrades, Weapons Unlock, over <strong>200 </strong>different upgrades (including rarity) available!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/b6803f5a97bce760617acbd25a1965b0.poster.avif?t=1768849144\" width=774 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/b6803f5a97bce760617acbd25a1965b0.webm?t=1768849144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/b6803f5a97bce760617acbd25a1965b0.mp4?t=1768849144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PERKS!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Perk System enables different mechanics on every run, Perks are an awesome way to try different builds and completely change the strategy for the run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/464e99fde8ef40e3a25543c4e0c4b19a.poster.avif?t=1768849144\" width=774 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/464e99fde8ef40e3a25543c4e0c4b19a.webm?t=1768849144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/464e99fde8ef40e3a25543c4e0c4b19a.mp4?t=1768849144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SHOP UPGRADES!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend your earned currency (souls) in upgrades for new and better runs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/0c38ff14555ce1d6237dc32dc09962ac.avif?t=1768849144\" width=745 height=779 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEADERBOARDS!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you be the best in the world?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ACHIEVEMENTS!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 40+ tracked achievements, can you get them all?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/e534b720bd0a9ebdfa8aa763e2e4abec.poster.avif?t=1768849144\" width=774 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/e534b720bd0a9ebdfa8aa763e2e4abec.webm?t=1768849144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157230/extras/e534b720bd0a9ebdfa8aa763e2e4abec.mp4?t=1768849144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow through the history as you progress, can you help Rabbit get back home?</p>",
